Clinton Cards Considering Restructuring, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 
2011-06-26T07:07:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-26/clinton-cards-considering-restructuring-sunday-times-reports.html
Clinton Cards Plc (CC/)  may be looking at
a restructuring which may lead to the company being taken
private and shop numbers being reduced, the  Sunday Times 
reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ben Martin in London at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
